    • Method Detail

      • getExperimentCaseResult

        protected static ExperimentCaseResult getExperimentCaseResult(String name,
                                           NativeJob nativeJob,
                                           File permanentHolderDirectory,
                                           File temporaryHolderDirectory,
                                           ExperimentHook hook)
                                                       throws IOException,
                                                              ExperimentQueryException,
                                                              ExperimentDataManipulationException,
                                                              ExperimentNotCompletedException
        Gets the experiment case result for the given native job If the experiment is not executing this method will limit itself to trying to retrieve the potentially existing result from the local store
        Parameters:
        name - a String with the name for this result
        nativeJob - the NativeJob that represents the underlying job
        permanentHolderDirectory - a File pointing to a directory relative to which this object can save permanent files, this directory must already exist
        temporaryHolderDirectory - a File pointing to a directory relative to which this object can save temporary files, this directory must already exist
        hook - the ExperimentHook to use when retrieving results, null if no hook should be used
        Returns:
        the ExperimentCase requested, or null it it cannot be obtained from the native system and it was not in the local store
        Throws:
        IOException - if there is a problem storing the result composed of the result files
        ExperimentQueryException - if the result could not be obtained from the native system
        ExperimentNotCompletedException - if this constructor was invoked before the experiment case has completed execution
        ExperimentDataManipulationException - if the experiment case result instance to be returned could not be created due to problem trying to store the result data
